In the investment game its not us vs. them. Its not the bulls vs. the bears. Its us vs Mr. Market. Therein lies a distinction.
An observation. Too many market pundits attack the other side of their invt proposition rather than detail the reasons (and specific strategies) for their own views.
To me the biggest obstacle to delivering superior invetment performance is the market itself (how we deal with Mr. Market) - not the opposite view of mine. Just my view.
